### Project Tutwiler - Scoring API Endpoints
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5239

### 1. Get BioImpactScore for a specific vulnerability (replace {id} with actual vulnerability ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/scoring/vulnerability/1
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get priority level distribution
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/scoring/distribution
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get top 10 critical vulnerabilities (default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/scoring/top-critical
Accept: application/json

### 4. Get top 20 critical vulnerabilities (custom limit)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/scoring/top-critical?limit=20
Accept: application/json

### 5. Get top 5 critical vulnerabilities
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/scoring/top-critical?limit=5
Accept: application/json

### 6. Get scoring statistics summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/scoring/stats
Accept: application/json

###
### EXISTING ENDPOINTS FOR TESTING WORKFLOW
###

### 7. Ingest vulnerabilities (prerequisite for analysis)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ingestion/full?daysBack=3
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Get ingestion stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ingestion/stats
Accept: application/json

### 9. Run batch analysis (this will create BioImpactScores)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/analysis/batch?limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Get analysis stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analysis/stats
Accept: application/json

